<!doctype html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>{% if title %}{{ title }} · {% endif %}{{ site.title }}</title>
  <meta name="description" content="{{ site.description }}" />
  <meta name="keywords" content="금융, 재테크, 증시, 투자 인사이트, 데일리 뉴스" />
  <link rel="canonical" href="{{ site.url }}" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <meta property="og:title" content="{{ site.title }}" />
  <meta property="og:description" content="{{ site.description }}" />
  <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
  <meta property="og:url" content="{{ site.url }}" />
  <meta property="og:site_name" content="{{ site.title }}" />
  <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
  <meta name="twitter:site" content="@martin" />
  <style>
    :root {
      font-family: 'Inter', 'Space Grotesk', system-ui, sans-serif;
      background-color: #030513;
      color: #f5f6ff;
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      min-height: 100vh;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #040712 0%, #02030a 45%, #041125 100%);
    }
    .app-shell {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: clamp(24px, 3vw, 40px) clamp(16px, 4vw, 64px) 56px;
    }
    header {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }
    .tagline {
      margin-top: 4px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }
    header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 3vw, 2.8rem);
      line-height: 1.1;
    }
    nav {
      display: flex;
      gap: 18px;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }
    nav a {
      color: #91b9ff;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .hero {
      padding: 24px;
      border-radius: 24px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top, rgba(144, 207, 255, 0.12), transparent 60%), rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      margin-bottom: 32px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
      gap: 24px;
    }
    .hero div {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
    }
    .hero strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 1.35rem;
      color: #ffffff;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }
    .layout-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 3fr) minmax(280px, 1fr);
      gap: clamp(24px, 3vw, 40px);
    }
    .issue-card {
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      padding: clamp(20px, 2vw, 32px);
      border-radius: 26px;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
      background: rgba(12, 17, 35, 0.85);
      box-shadow: 0 28px 80px rgba(3,5,13,0.55);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .issue-card::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      border-radius: 26px;
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.05), transparent 60%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .issue-card-content {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }
    .issue-card h3 { margin-top: 0; font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 2vw, 1.9rem); line-height: 1.3; }
    .issue-card p { line-height: 1.7; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); }
    .issue-meta, .issue-source { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; font-size: 0.85rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65); flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 12px; }
    .tags { display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:10px; margin-top:18px; }
    .tag { font-size:0.8rem; padding:6px 12px; border-radius:999px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); }
    .ad-slot {
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 22px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
      color: #a8c9ff;
      margin-bottom: 26px;
    }
    .ad-slot span { display: block; font-size: 0.8rem; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .ad-slot strong { font-size: 1rem; color: #ffffff; }
    aside ul { padding-left: 20px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75); }
    footer { margin-top: 60px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); padding-top: 20px; font-size: 0.8rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:12px; justify-content:space-between; }
    .privacy-links a { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); }
    @media (max-width: 960px) {
      .layout-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      nav { justify-content: flex-start; }
    }
  </style>
  <script type="application/ld+json">
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "NewsMediaOrganization",
      "name": "{{ site.title }}",
      "url": "{{ site.url }}",
      "description": "{{ site.description }}",
      "publisher": {
        "@type": "Organization",
        "name": "{{ site.title }}"
      }
    }
  </script>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="app-shell">
    <header>
      <div>
        <h1>{{ site.title }}</h1>
        <p class="tagline">{{ site.description }}</p>
      </div>
      <nav aria-label="Quick links">
        <a href="{{ site.url }}">홈</a>
        <a href="mailto:martin@example.com">문의</a>
        <a href="{{ site.url }}/privacy">프라이버시</a>
      </nav>
    </header>
    <div class="hero">
      <div>
        <strong>Daily Market Radar</strong>
        <p>매일 오전 6시(서울 기준) 글로벌 금융 데이터를 정량/정성적으로 분석해 한 장으로 정리합니다.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <strong>AdSense-ready layout</strong>
        <p>광고는 메인 읽기 흐름을 방해하지 않도록 사이드바와 콘텐츠 사이에 자연스럽게 배치합니다.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <strong>SEO optimized</strong>
        <p>OpenGraph, Schema, canonical 등 검색 엔진 최적화 요소를 내장했습니다.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="layout-grid">
      <main>
        {{ content | safe }}
      </main>
      <aside>
        <div class="ad-slot" aria-label="AdSense preview">
          <span>광고 슬롯</span>
          <strong>AdSense 300x250</strong>
          <p>프리미엄 사이드바 공간에 숨김 없이 노출. 방문자가 글을 읽는 데 방해되지 않도록 디자인되어 있습니다.</p>
        </div>
        <section aria-labelledby="why-updated">
          <h3 id="why-updated">Daily signal tracker</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>오전 06:00 KST 글로벌 종합 리포트(금리·원자재·정책)</li>
            <li>Tagging system으로 빠른 분류 및 검색</li>
            <li>Cloudflare Pages 빌드 로그를 기반으로 자동 알림</li>
          </ul>
        </section>
      </aside>
    </div>
    <footer>
      <div>
        © {{ today.now | year }} {{ site.author }} · Cloudflare Pages · Eleventy
      </div>
      <div class="privacy-links">
        <a href="{{ site.url }}/privacy">Privacy</a>
        <a href="{{ site.url }}/disclaimer">Disclaimer</a>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
